<emphasis italics="true" pageId="56" pageNumber="57">P.A. Rydberg 1385</emphasis>
(lectotype, designated here: NY [NY00138953] isotypes: GH [GH00077424], H [acc. # 1087075], NDG [NDG45091], NEB [NEB-V-0000607], NY [NY00138952], US [US00027625, acc. # 210385; US02828882, acc. # 210353]).
